WEBVTT

36:07.510 --> 36:09.430 line:80%
Qianqian, this Guo is

36:09.460 --> 36:10.760 line:80%
selling water-injected meat.

36:10.760 --> 36:12.120 line:80%
He even added borax.

36:12.120 --> 36:13.830 line:80%
It looks fresh but tastes rotten.

36:13.830 --> 36:14.240 line:80%
Stop shouting!

36:14.240 --> 36:15.830 line:80%
He's notorious in our trade.
